      "id": "PopularPost2726",
      "post_content": "One star from me, rather than 0.5 ignominy, since it can hypothetically be better than [Prodigal Pyromancer](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Prodigal Pyromancer) in a deck with artifact creature token producers. That's still something of a reach though.  \n  \nDoes if bother anyone else that red creatures have been portrayed as dumb and liable to fail at their one job since day one? It just reinforces the negative and pernicious stereotype that Red = Stupid. Bah.",
